data.description: Are you looking for a serene location with unmatched convenience? This expansive ranch home is close to Ga 400, UNG, Northeast Ga Medical in Lumpkin, Dahlonega, Dawsonville, Lake Lanier and more!   This home offers comfort and functuality with a ginormous bonus room that could be transitioned in to many options such as a great school room, office, playroom, craft room or as it is now, the teenage headquarters!   The home features a sturdy metal roof, and also has a long covered front porch that leads to a large screened in porch with an additional uncovered porch. Whether you're hosting gatherings indoors or embracing the outdoors, ample entertainment space awaits.  Every room in this house is spacious, this home is functional and comfortable. Conventionly located close to Blackburn Elementary, and also it is about 10 miles from University of North Ga, it is 7 miles to the outlet mall in Dawsonville, and about an hour/half from Hartsfield Jackson. When you see this home,  you'll think Home Sweet Home!
